      • updateNotification

        public  updateNotification(Notification notification)
                         throws java.net.URISyntaxException
        PUT /notifications : Updates an existing notification.
        Parameters:
        notification - the notification to update
        Returns:
        the ResponseEntity with status 200 (OK) and with body the updated notification, or with status 400 (Bad Request) if the notification is not valid, or with status 500 (Internal Server Error) if the notification couldnt be updated
        Throws:
        java.net.URISyntaxException - if the Location URI syntax is incorrect
